<ul>
<li>Purpose and Theories of Contract Law</li>

<li>Elements of a Contract</li>

<li>Pre-contractual Instruments: the step before a formal contract</li>

<li>Drafting of Agreements: Preliminary Terms</li>

<li>Drafting of Agreements: Operative Clauses</li>

<li>Drafting of Agreements: Boilerplate Clauses</li>
</ul>

